{"tid":982522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JENNIE對D隊友冇連登仔講到咁差","createTime":"2019-01-15T07:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T07:08:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"36127685e3714a14a7d0359141cf4c87b2a2f99d","tid":982522,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3830/d3830111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3830%2Fd3830111.jpg&h=71215c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK泰國籍成員Lisa是IG追蹤人數最多的南韓女星。（圖／翻攝自Lisa IG）<br />\n<br />\nLisa在Instagram追蹤人數短短7個月就突破1300萬人，高人氣可見一斑。不過美貌和實力兼具的她，近來卻被南韓網友攻擊，謾罵內容更是充滿種族歧視，像是「她上妝看起來像俄羅斯娃娃，案卸妝後就是一般泰國女人。」、「呵呵，韓國的化妝術真是太神奇了。」、「誰在乎她？她就是從泰國來賺錢的，根本不應該在這裡出現。」粉絲為保護Lisa，也發起串聯讓「RespectLisa」話題登上推特熱門趨勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3830/d3830113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3830%2Fd3830113.jpg&h=33045be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK成員感情非常好。（圖／翻攝自BLACKPINK IG）<br />\n日前BLACKPINK在Lisa的故鄉泰國曼谷舉辦演唱會，成員們似乎也看到了近來的惡意評論，成員Jennie在台上表示：「Lisa是一個強大、健康、積極向上的女孩，我想在Lisa的家鄉告訴每一位：她，由我們來守護！」霸氣宣言感動許多粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n妮妮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73659c8d68ec30b1c0d2ba3b92639688b76bd10f","tid":982522,"uid":7903,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"你估個個僱主都好似羅允彤咁打鳩個工人姐姐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993eba242b6e9d9f97c6545405baba4560418d77","tid":982522,"uid":202385,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"幾時屌jennie隊友<br />\n不嬲淨係